title: [Maelstrom Bay, Underwater]
description: Light green water above, deep green water below, green water all around.  A reef covered with club-fingered coral forms a wall to the west.  A wide patch of sargassum on the surface blocks the moonlight.  The long, green, flat-bladed streamers hanging beneath the sargassum sway and undulate sinuously.
